dc_title_s: Tax Parcels City of Madison, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents tax parcels in the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2020. [This data layer is used by the Property Lookup, Neighborhood Development Plans, Neighborhood Development Plan Resource Viewer, Generalized Future Land Use, What is Density, City of Madison Historic Districts and Landmarks, Zoning Districts, Urban Design Districts and Development Information applications. NOTE: the City’s Open Data content is updated daily and is current to the best of our ability. Any “Last Updated Date” dates on the site reflect when the specific web page was updated – NOT the data.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data, please visit: [https://data-cityofmadison.opendata.arcgis.com/]
